::Sideswipe sees Prebon use Spears as a shield::
Sidesiwpe: Damn it!
::He transforms to car mode and trys to run Prebon over, making sure not to 
hit Spears.  Andromeda sees the shots coming, she gets hit by 2 of them.  She 
then saw Ignatius trying to hit her::
Andromeda: Too bad pal, I'm an eagle too!
::She transforms to beast mode and flies up, about to dive bomb Ignatius with 
her talons.  Some holes get drilled in Ratchet, but his tough hide protects 
him from the full blunt of the blow he tranforms to robot mode and fires 8 
shots from each blaster at Hammer.  Bluestreak is hit by 8 of the shots and 
throws 6 daggers at Bullet.  When they see Tamron being formed, They all fire 
at him::
